{"data":[{"id":562997756,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562997756","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546170861,"updated_time":1546317139,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":566,"comment_count":55,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"我不讨厌逐梦者 因为我也是其中一员\u003cbr\u003e我也曾趴在图书馆的书桌上\u003cbr\u003e幻想自己成为第一个拿到菲奖的中国人\u003cbr\u003e所以我努力充实自己\u003cbr\u003e在课余时间拼命阅读大学数学\u003cbr\u003e给自己打造好坚实的数学基础\u003cbr\u003e是的 我也是一个高中生\u003cbr\u003e一个数学狂热分子\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e很抱歉 我并不相信你\u003cbr\u003e因为我深知哥猜的难度\u003cbr\u003e它绝非一位未经过大学专业化训练的人所能证明\u003cbr\u003e现在已经不是19 20世纪那个黄金年代了\u003cbr\u003e一个人就能独自研究出改变数学界的东西\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e数学王冠上的明珠 是屹立百年不倒的世界难题\u003cbr\u003e他的题目只要是一位中学生也能看懂\u003cbr\u003e但他的证明却不是简单的数页证明就可以结束的\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e对数学有兴趣 是好事\u003cbr\u003e我惊讶你的勇气 \u003cbr\u003e希望你在1号之后仍然保持对数学的热爱\u003cbr\u003e学习了庞杂的现代数学体系后\u003cbr\u003e从小猜想 小结论开始\u003cbr\u003e再次向它发起进攻\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e你的格局太小了 \u003cbr\u003e一个认为自己能改变世界的人\u003cbr\u003e怎么还在考虑自己是否能上清华北大\u003cbr\u003e不能上又如何 \u003cbr\u003e真正的大数学家 就是在野鸡大学读书\u003cbr\u003e也无法埋没它的才能\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e其实我也很期待此生能看见哥猜的证明\u003cbr\u003e如果你的证明真是对的\u003cbr\u003e我向你表达我的歉意与敬意\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e不要暴露自己的个人信息\u003cbr\u003e会有你无法预见的后果\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e最后的最后 失败不可怕 年轻有失败的资本\u003cbr\u003e//\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e证明已看……一股浓浓的民科气息……意料之中吧…错误已经有人指出了，我就不说了\u003cbr\u003e但希望题主还是要保持对数学的热爱\u003cbr\u003e但是从此要脚踏实地好好读数学\u003cbr\u003e把哥猜埋在心里吧\u003cbr\u003e数学不是想象的那么简单\u003cbr\u003e每一位民科都觉得自己是世界上最伟大的科学家，最后抛弃了家人朋友事业，沉溺于自己的伪科学\u003cbr\u003e希望题主不要成为他们，高考考到数学系吧","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我不讨厌逐梦者 因为我也是其中一员 我也曾趴在图书馆的书桌上 幻想自己成为第一个拿到菲奖的中国人 所以我努力充实自己 在课余时间拼命阅读大学数学 给自己打造好坚实的数学基础 是的 我也是一个高中生 一个数学狂热分子 很抱歉 我并不相信你 因为我深知哥…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=68\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/3